Botswana Air Crash Kills 8 Foreign Nationals in Okavango

-- B y   J e r r y   B u n g u
-- 
2011-10-18T11:50:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-18/botswana-air-crash-kills-8-foreign-nationals-in-okavango-1-.html
Eight people, including seven
tourists, died in a plane crash in  Botswana ’s Okavango Delta
wildlife area on Oct. 14, the Civil Aviation Authority of
Botswana said in a statement.  The dead include four Swedes, two French nationals and two
people from the U.K., Gaborone’s Mmegi newspaper reported
yesterday. Four people survived the crash.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jerry Bungu in Gaborone at 
 jbungu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  